<GRAPHIC>
<P>
Photo, Shadow of her former self -- Gail Escott poses Wednesday in London while 
her husband, Ian, and her son, Daniel, share one of her old coats. Escott, 30, 
shed 168 pounds and won the "Slimmer of the Year" contest. Associated Press 
</P>
