<P>
COMPANY: GAF Building Materials Corp., Irwindale 
</P>
<P>
TYPE OF BUSINESS: Building materials manufacturer 
</P>
<P>
PENALTY: $15,000 
</P>
<P>
VIOLATION: Failure to control nitrogen-oxide emissions from a furnace 
</P>
