Galleria on a busy day. Below, Sgt. Mark Distaso, left, and Bunzey monitor a 
chase after a suspected shoplifting. ; Photo, Officer Maurice Bunzey checks in 
during patrol of Glendale mall. RICARDO DeARATANHA / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
