arm. United Press International; Chart, The early prognosis is that San 
Francisco pitcher Dave Dravecky will be able to begin rehabilitation in six 
weeks, with the humerus bone healing fully early next year., PATRICIA MITCHELL 
/ Los Angeles Times ; Photo, COLOR, Dravecky returning home. 
