<P>
EARTHQUAKE JARS ARMENIA 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
From Reuters 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>
<P>
MOSCOW 
</P>
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
An earthquake hit rural districts of Soviet Armenia near Yerevan, the capital, 
on Wednesday but caused no damage or casualties, the official news agency Tass 
reported. 
</P>
<P>
An earthquake last December destroyed several towns and cities in the northwest 
of the republic, killing at least 25,000 people. 
</P>
