<P>
Israeli officials are depriving the 700,000 Palestinians in the occupied Gaza 
Strip of adequate medical care as an additional means of battling the Arab 
uprising, a group of doctors charged. Members of the group -- the Assn. of 
Israeli and Palestinian Physicians for Human Rights -- said at a news 
