ELECTION FRAUD; ORANGE COUNTY -- ELECTIONS -- 1988; ARRESTS -- ORANGE COUNTY; 
VOTER REGISTRATION; DEMOCRATIC PARTY (ORANGE COUNTY) 
</P>
