<HEADLINE>
<P>
EARNINGS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
TouchStone Software Corp. posted net earnings of $10,078 for the second 
quarter, a 49% increase compared to the year-earlier $6,752. Revenue rose 38% 
to $351,780 from $254,017. TouchStone earned $39,650 for the six-month period, 
48% above the $26,758 for the first half of 1988. Revenue increased 22% to 
$703,348 from $575,661. 
</P>
